Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.28,0:00:06.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}With the Millennium Puzzle complete,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.91,0:00:10.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The young boy Yugi Mutou became a master of the Dark Games.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.51,0:00:15.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He was challenged by a person that has a Millennium Item like him,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.16,0:00:21.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}the owner of the Millennium Eye, Pegasus, and went to the Duelist Kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.83,0:00:27.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To save the soul of Sugoroku, that was stolen by him.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.93,0:00:33.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Together with his friends and with his other self.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.33,0:00:43.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A magazine page I can't finish reading.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.21,0:00:50.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to read it, but somehow I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.07,0:00:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Game software is stacked in the corner of the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.85,0:01:04.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I don't play them, will they become meaningless?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.78,0:01:12.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just beyond the table, and I'm trying to talk with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.60,0:01:19.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A never changing facial expression is on your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.92,0:01:26.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I'm right here with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.17,0:01:33.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They can't reach, they can't reach, these feelings of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.97,0:01:40.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what's really important?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.99,0:01:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(301,136)}Clash! Blue Eyes vs. Red Eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.09,0:02:01.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seto Kaiba is coming to my island?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.64,0:02:04.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You need not worry! We'll catch him in no time!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.26,0:02:08.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kaiba can't hide in the Duelist Kingdom forever...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.89,0:02:13.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! You aren't to lay a {\i1}hand{\i0} on Seto Kaiba!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.44,0:02:24.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The contract states that I have to defeat Yugi-boy and that will be no problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.33,0:02:29.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When that happens, Kaiba Corporation will be ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.63,0:02:37.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Kaiba Corporation's advanced technology and the genius mind....
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.76,0:02:40.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...of Seto Kaiba will belong to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.72,0:02:50.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seto Kaiba... I'll be waiting for our meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.53,0:03:04.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yugi... his battle style is incomparable...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.83,0:03:08.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The card I just drew...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.62,0:03:11.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is The Sealed One, Exodia!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.17,0:03:17.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Light of Hellfire!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.63,0:03:18.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Exodo Flame!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.05,0:03:24.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now matter how strong a card is...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.55,0:03:27.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's useless if you can't connect your heart with that card.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.60,0:03:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When you connect your heart with the cards, miracles happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.44,0:03:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want to battle with him once again!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.90,0:03:41.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But before that, there's someone that I want to defeat with this duel disc system.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.24,0:03:51.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.17,0:03:55.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To take control of Kaiba Corporation...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.21,0:03:58.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have to attack those traitors...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.17,0:04:01.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And the man that kidnapped Mokuba.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.05,0:04:04.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Pegasus J. Crawford!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.85,0:04:09.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm going to defeat you with my own hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.41,0:04:29.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Bakura-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.62,0:04:30.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at this...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.33,0:04:35.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One of the needles of the Millennium Ring is pointing to Pegasus' Castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.92,0:04:41.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.55,0:04:45.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was the same when I was transferred to Domino High.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.01,0:04:52.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}From today onwards, we'll have a new student with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.93,0:04:54.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How 'bout {\i1}this{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.89,0:04:57.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's your turn, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.11,0:05:03.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-That day, it was pointing to your Millennium Puzzle.\N{\i1}-What's with that card?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.94,0:05:04.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Shit~!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.24,0:05:11.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, the Millennium Ring is pointing to the Millennium Item that Pegasus owns?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.95,0:05:13.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Millennium Item?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.50,0:05:18.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe the Millennium Ring can locate the other Millennium Items.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.59,0:05:23.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What exactly are the Millennium Items? Where did they came from?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.05,0:05:26.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, I don't know anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.64,0:05:39.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My Millennium Puzzle is not the only Millennium Item that exists.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.11,0:05:50.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When I completed the Millennium Puzzle, inside of me,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.62,0:05:53.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I discovered the existence of another me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.16,0:05:56.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I would like to know... this puzzle...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.71,0:05:58.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I can understand this puzzle...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.58,0:06:02.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I will be able to save my grandfather from the Dark World.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.63,0:06:05.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wait until then, Grandpa.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.56,0:06:23.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.74,0:06:30.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is it? Doing such a thing at this time at night?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.20,0:06:31.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.59,0:06:50.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.89,0:06:55.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while... Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.02,0:06:58.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.10,0:07:01.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here... Kaiba-kun's Deck...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.81,0:07:03.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I saved it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.48,0:07:08.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For now, I'll thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.95,0:07:13.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba-kun, you understand the heart of the cards now, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.16,0:07:18.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.00,0:07:22.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, I don't have the answer for this...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.54,0:07:26.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To protect Mokuba and Kaiba Corporation...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.96,0:07:28.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will defeat Pegasus.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.13,0:07:31.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By any means necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.59,0:07:32.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.14,0:07:39.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute, Kaiba!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.35,0:07:46.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All people in Duelist Kingdom have to work hard to win 10 Star Chips...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.82,0:07:49.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...in order to {\i1}fight{\i0} that same Pegasus!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.19,0:07:54.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter what your reasons are, I won't forgive you if you pass over us!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.83,0:08:03.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.21,0:08:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you alright, Jounouchi-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.00,0:08:06.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.00,0:08:11.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi, it can't be that you are participating in this too, can it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.26,0:08:13.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't underestimate me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.80,0:08:16.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I may not look like much, but I was the Best Eight of a tournament!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.01,0:08:19.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was the {\i1}Regional{\i0} Championship Tournament, right...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.27,0:08:25.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If even someone like {\i1}you{\i0} is a Duelist here, this island's level must be pretty low.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.44,0:08:27.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.69,0:08:29.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it, Jounouchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.78,0:08:36.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Kaiba!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.57,0:08:39.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am not the same person as before!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.62,0:08:45.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true, Kaiba-kun! Jounouchi defeated Mai Kujaku-san and Dinosaur Ryuzaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.42,0:08:54.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fight! If you want to battle Pegasus, first you will have to face me off!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.97,0:08:56.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop with that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.22,0:08:58.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true! You're gonna hurt yourself...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.47,0:09:02.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the problem, Kaiba? Here and now, fight with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.02,0:09:04.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.27,0:09:09.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will shatter that glass confidence you have, until there's nothing left.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.69,0:09:10.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.11,0:09:16.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry... this battle won't put your star chips at stake.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.78,0:09:23.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will only use Jounouchi's energy to test my new duel disk system.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.66,0:09:26.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,New duel disk system?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.26,0:09:40.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Put that on your left arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.43,0:09:41.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.68,0:09:46.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel Disk... the new card battle machine that I've created...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.27,0:09:51.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even without a Duel Ring, it can create a field using a virtual simulation system.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.07,0:09:55.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First, fix the Deck Holder on your left arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.74,0:09:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what next?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.20,0:09:59.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just watch!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.12,0:10:05.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Set your cards in the deck holder for its activation.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.62,0:10:13.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Draw the card from the Deck Holder, and set the card you will use in the duel on the Duel Disk.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.30,0:10:19.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After that, throw the Duel Disk in the field where you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.59,0:10:20.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.56,0:10:26.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Minotaur!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.23,0:10:31.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The card's data is read by the Duel Disk...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.61,0:10:34.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the Hyper 3-D Engine projects its image...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.94,0:10:36.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's shown as a Solid Vision!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.20,0:10:44.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing! Kaiba-kun just evolved the card battles!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.26,0:11:04.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Interesting!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.72,0:11:06.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll battle with this card!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.52,0:11:09.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.89,0:11:10.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.40,0:11:18.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go! Armor Lizard!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.82,0:11:25.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Minotaur! Cut the enemy down!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.00,0:11:34.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! It didn't work!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.67,0:11:35.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.63,0:11:36.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.14,0:11:45.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My card was...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.51,0:11:49.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When the monster is destroyed, pull back the duel disk.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.98,0:11:54.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until you have played a monster, I'll pass my turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.86,0:12:01.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't look down on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.61,0:12:02.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just watch!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.03,0:12:04.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.08,0:12:10.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Flame Swordsman!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.33,0:12:14.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's about Attack Points, he's got more!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.58,0:12:16.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fighting Spirit Flame Sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.29,0:12:20.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't! Minotaur is strong against Flame Attacks!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.59,0:12:25.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Iron Axe!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.85,0:12:27.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Flame Swordsman is destroyed!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.31,0:12:31.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it. You've gotta be the worst Duelist in existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.52,0:12:36.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Fusion and Centaur cards...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.11,0:12:38.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel Disk set!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.58,0:12:55.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop looking down at me like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.00,0:12:57.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.67,0:13:01.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Barbarian #2!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.38,0:13:06.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Axe Raider!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.14,0:13:09.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bull Devil!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.01,0:13:11.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Garoozis!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.68,0:13:13.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cavern Genie! Ogre Rock!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.86,0:13:19.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rude Kaiser!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.79,0:13:34.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to the confidence you had before, Jounouchi? Gone {\i1}already{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.12,0:13:39.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's useless... I can't win like this... our levels are way too different...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.34,0:13:40.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.46,0:13:43.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stand up, Jounouchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.76,0:13:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.17,0:13:48.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! I don't want to see you like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.68,0:13:50.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.35,0:13:52.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.06,0:13:54.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I still won't give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.06,0:13:56.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The battle begins now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.27,0:14:00.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch closely, my Red-Eyes Black Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.11,0:14:09.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.32,0:14:10.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His trump is here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.24,0:14:12.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.66,0:14:13.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dark Flame Bullet!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.58,0:14:18.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.33,0:14:22.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Getting excited because you succeeded getting through one turn...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.88,0:14:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That{\i0}'s why I said you're the worst Duelist in existence!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.47,0:14:27.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.59,0:14:32.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been holding onto the card your friend got back for me in this deck.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.44,0:14:39.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Appear, Blue-Eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.86,0:14:45.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prepare yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.32,0:14:48.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Burst Stream of Destruction!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.83,0:15:02.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.46,0:15:04.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.76,0:15:09.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.34,0:15:12.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you learn your lesson after dueling me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.89,0:15:16.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With your incompetence, I don't know how you made it this far.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.02,0:15:21.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi... it really suits you to be on your knees.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.11,0:15:25.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like a loser dog unable to stand up after a single loss.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.53,0:15:26.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.07,0:15:30.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? What do you think you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.91,0:15:33.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know why Jounouchi is fighting...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.87,0:15:36.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say anything if you know nothing of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.25,0:15:40.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! Jounouchi-kun's sister's eyes are...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.92,0:15:43.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it! Don't say anything more!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.13,0:15:50.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even the weakest duelist on this island has a reason to fight, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.76,0:15:55.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The most important thing here is if you can protect that reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.68,0:15:59.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi... it was a huge mistake to fight me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.39,0:16:02.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now you've got the eyes of a loser dog after fighting me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.15,0:16:07.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You cannot stand up as a Duelist anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.23,0:16:09.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba-kun... why are you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.99,0:16:13.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pegasus's castle. That's where {\i1}he{\i0} awaits.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.78,0:16:16.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pegasus J. Crawford...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.24,0:16:21.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The creator of Duel Monsters, a man with a terrifying power.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.79,0:16:28.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His mind created the rules... In his hands all the cards were created.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.76,0:16:34.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In this island, to get in that castle, all duelists are collecting stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.72,0:16:40.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's only what the god of the card kingdom wants them to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.64,0:16:47.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi, even with your skills, defeating Pegasus is impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.11,0:16:52.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've seen him in the past once in a Duel...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.28,0:16:55.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... I can't call that a duel.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.45,0:17:01.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was in New York Duel Stadium, with the fight of the King of Duelists!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.08,0:17:05.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was invited as a special guest to that battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.21,0:17:10.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pegasus's opponent was America's Number One Card Professor, Keith Howard.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.55,0:17:16.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because he was always pursuing big prizes in money, he was known as "Bandit Keith".
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.10,0:17:21.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Fightin' with {\i1}you{\i0} will be an honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.22,0:17:26.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Well... when this duel is over, I'll be recognized as the world's number one.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.73,0:17:29.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Amazing! Who's gonna win?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.49,0:17:34.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I drew a good card...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.41,0:17:39.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hey, what are you doing? The duel already started!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.16,0:17:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pegasus just looked down on Keith and wrote on a piece of paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.29,0:17:48.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And called a kid that was seated behind me....
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.09,0:17:50.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...to play in his place.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.05,0:17:52.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}W-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.55,0:17:54.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't screw with me, Pegasus!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.76,0:17:57.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I’m not doing anything of the sort.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.26,0:18:01.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This young boy will duel with you in my place.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.31,0:18:03.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}D-Do you think I can do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.18,0:18:08.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No problem. If you follow the instruction on this memo, you'll win.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.36,0:18:12.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pegasus!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.94,0:18:15.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hello, Kaiba-boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.57,0:18:19.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh.. yeah... I read the proposal you made me...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.03,0:18:24.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Card Battle Simulator System... I found it incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.12,0:18:30.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let's work together with Kaiba Corporation to make it real.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.54,0:18:33.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you'd rather run away than lose to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.67,0:18:37.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't matter... as long as I get the prize...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.38,0:18:40.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll use this card, ya damn brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.26,0:18:46.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let me see... when you play that card, I have to play this card in Attack Mode.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.56,0:18:47.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}W-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.14,0:18:50.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It seems that I win with this attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.98,0:18:56.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Impossible! He knew all that I had in my hand in advance?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.57,0:19:02.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh my God! Oh my God!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.20,0:19:08.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tom wins!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.96,0:19:11.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He used some kind of trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.17,0:19:18.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know if the Duel Disks will be enough to win over this trick...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.88,0:19:19.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pegasus...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.55,0:19:22.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Alright, I use this card.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.89,0:19:25.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Devil Dragon card, am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.31,0:19:26.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.31,0:19:30.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I already knew that you would play this card.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.02,0:19:33.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That power... I have seen it...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.77,0:19:36.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba-kun... You...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.90,0:19:40.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This fight that you had with Jounouchi-kun was to...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.53,0:19:43.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi... I'm going to Pegasus's place...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.45,0:19:46.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To defeat Pegasus and also...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.04,0:19:48.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To take back what is mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.62,0:19:56.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba! Just like you, we too have things that are precious and we don't want to lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.38,0:20:01.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pegasus will be defeated by me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.05,0:20:03.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, I'll say it in a different way...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.47,0:20:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to Pegasus' castle {\i1}before{\i0} anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.57,0:20:23.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome, Kaiba-boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.16,0:20:32.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After being defeated by Kaiba-kun, Jounouchi finds himself in a great pinch!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.37,0:20:38.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The former US Champ, Bandit Keith, plans to trap Jounouchi in a match.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.25,0:20:43.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keith's followers ambushed Jounouchi and dragged him to a Graveyard Field where he has to fight with Ghost Kotsuzuka.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.76,0:20:47.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! You can't accept a duel in this condition!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.22,0:20:50.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: "Terror! Call of the Living Dead"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.89,0:20:52.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel Standby!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.09,0:21:02.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The flask shines bright
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.33,0:21:11.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}waiting in the Science Lab
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.70,0:21:20.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}By rubbing our cold hands together...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.94,0:21:27.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}They will become warm
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.67,0:21:33.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}An energy shower
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.25,0:21:37.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It'll shower all over you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.31,0:21:46.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I will support your lonely back
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.53,0:21:50.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}An energy shower
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.51,0:21:54.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You're not alone
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.17,0:22:04.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Because you're surrounded by a ring of friendship
